node.title: Police arrest woman associated with Christchurch protest
node.description: Police have arrested the 63-year-old driver of a vehicle associated with a protest group outside a Christchurch Police Station.
node.content:
["Police have arrested a 63-year-old driver of a vehicle associated with a protest group outside the Christchurch Central Police Station.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Marika Khabazi\n
", "In a statement, Police said they made attempts to stop the driver's vehicle, but the woman failed to comply.", "The driver's behaviour caused Police to become concerned and they stopped the vehicle a short time later.", "Police then apprehended the driver and impounded the vehicle.", "A 63-year-old female driver has been charged with multiple driving infringements including failing to stop for Police, dangerous driving, resisting arrest, and refusing a blood sample."]
